comment:
* Used for receiving notifications from the SpeechRecognizer about the device support status for
 * the given recognition request.

methods.name: void onSupportResult(@NonNull RecognitionSupport recognitionSupport)
methods.comment: Notifies the caller about the support for the given request.

methods.name: void onError(@SpeechRecognizer.RecognitionError int error)
methods.comment: Notifies the caller about an error during the recognition support request
